BHP’s Mozal Smelter Needs Extra 500 to 600 Megawatts, STv Says

-- B y   F r e d   K a t e r e r e
-- 
2011-02-23T12:58:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/bhp-s-mozal-smelter-needs-extra-500-to-600-megawatts-stv-says.html
  BHP Billiton Ltd .’s Mozal aluminum
smelter in Mozambique needs an additional 500 to 600 megawatts
of power for the third phase of its expansion, STv reported,
citing Mike Fraser, Mozal’s asset president.  Fraser told the Maputo-based broadcaster the company was
negotiating with the government and state-run power utility
Electricidade de Mocambique over its power requirements.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Katerere in Maputo at 
 fkaterere@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  